

=Bio=

As Member of ATTAC Germany and activist she founded the "Berlin Water Table" in 2006  that has won the yet only referendum in Berlin for water (2011), also founding member of GiB (Gemeingut in BürgerInnenhand = Commons in citizen's hands) and member of the European Water Movement.


